<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="img/png" href="/favicon.png"/>
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/fonts/Atkinson/Atkinson-Hyperlegible-Regular.woff2"
      as="font"
      type="font/woff2"
      crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/fonts/Atkinson/Atkinson-Hyperlegible-Bold.woff2"
      as="font"
      type="font/woff2"
      crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/fonts/Atkinson/Atkinson-Hyperlegible-Italic.woff2"
      as="font"
      type="font/woff2"
      crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/fonts/Atkinson/Atkinson-Hyperlegible-BoldItalic.woff2"
      as="font"
      type="font/woff2"
      crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="@root/styles/_base.scss">
    <title>{{ title if title else "It's Slinkity time" }}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="layout__outline">
      <p>You'll notice this page is wrapped in a layout. This pulls in a few parameters using
        <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/docs/data-cascade/">11ty's data cascade:</a>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <code>title</code>
          uses the "title" attribute from our page's front matter.</li>
        <li>
          <code>content | safe</code>
          renders our page.</li>
      </ul>
      {{ content | safe }}
    </main>
  </body>
</html>